Using Verilator 5.007 devel rev v5.006-101-g47a7e758

```
`timescale 1ns/1ps

module time();

	initial begin
		#5ms;
		$display("finish at %t", $realtime);
		$finish();
	end

endmodule
```
results in `finish at            705032704`
but 5000000000 would have been expected. Looks like uint32 - overflow `5e9 % 2**32 == 705032704`
